Name: PooSky
About the game: You live in a cloudless country on the special clouds. But they came, and you run away.. You have no choice. And you can not win. You can only run for fun these assfaces. How long do you survive? What will be your last race? This game is an allegory. You are Pisyun who runs to a meeting of a good game. Obstacles are indie projects, which every day more and more. You try, you search, but every time you stammer on another 'masterpiece'. The game is specially performed in the most beloved program of indie developers and it is at this 'level' Features: - Peculiar protagonist, who expresses the identity of a community; - A unique antagonist that you will remember for a long time; - Rhythmic soundtrack; - Top Achivements; - Deep sense.
